{"tid":1955334,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「看透了」匯豐控股0005的一生","createTime":"2020-04-02T11:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T12:35:30.000Z","uid":70888,"like":103,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bd320cb05d0343d1f91c3f2ca067b5026a2b76b5","tid":1955334,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:48:43.000Z","msg":"匯豐150蚊，大戶開始獲利，散戶瘋狂追入<br />\n匯豐120蚊，大行調低目標價，散戶繼續買入<br />\n匯豐100蚊，大戶持續拋貨，散戶嘗試撈底<br />\n匯豐80蚊，股價由高位跌了接近一半，散戶繼續strong hold，深信今次見底了<br />\n匯豐65蚊，湯文亮(紀惠集團行政總裁)教導老友用原來買樓的1200萬全數買入匯豐，期待150蚊來臨<br />\n匯豐50蚊，大戶繼續沽空，部分散戶忍痛止蝕<br />\n匯豐40蚊，湯文亮老友聯絡不上湯文亮<br />\n匯豐33蚊，青姐流下了第一滴眼淚，湯文亮老友留下了遺書<br />\n匯豐10蚊，IFC發生多宗墜樓命案，慘絕人寰<br />\n匯豐1蚊，巴菲特終於說：『老天，價值投資很難玩！』<br />\n連登仔：『開始止蝕了！』"},{"pid":"c907935b7a9b079e1d8bd3ae0d6df8c1a0e4f1b7","tid":1955334,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581e7bd0c46ec591cd6a636b4ff67c13da6404a1","tid":1955334,"uid":22007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:51:41.000Z","msg":"黑洞底留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff3041f23779361e7d2ad9f99e45eec72559431","tid":1955334,"uid":33728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"345ea720b5940fd97ec849af5e34865ae47e6d64","tid":1955334,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:53:05.000Z","msg":"掉過20我直播裸跑啊仆街"},{"pid":"5b8afdb4845e7625c7c8fbd12cdfaa27b56b4a8b","tid":1955334,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d76bc043e376baa5252b6655678e1fa0e37c3d","tid":1955334,"uid":81273,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:53:43